data.description:
This home has it all!  4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, renovated in 2022.  Everything in this home was updated.  New kitchen with granite counters, new cabinets, new appliances, and new floors.  The spacious primary suite has a new bathroom with a walk in closet.  With this home there are no updates needed!  Conveniently located close to schools, shopping, and downtown Bridgeport, this a home you don't want to miss.

Creative financing available.
